snippet.title: Jason Momoa BREAKS his trident & chooses me! Ft. Amber Heard & James Wan | Aquaman PH
snippet.description:
HE IS INTENSE! He was running all over the place, screaming at the top of his lungs and breaking stuff! ...Well.... His trident at least. :))

AMBER HEARD. I had a short convo with Amber Heard. Find out what her favorite color is! Lol.
